# Atom Editor: Customization for Haskell

First verify, that the following Haskell packages are in the search path:

* ghc-mod
* stylish-haskell
* hlint

Install the following atom packages:

* language-haskell
* haskell-ghc-mod 
* ide-haskell
* ide-haskell-cabal
* autocomplete-haskell
* ide-haskell-repl
* term3